Package it.kibo.fp.lib

package it.kibo.fp.lib
  • Class
    Description
    AnsiColors
    The enumeration AnsiColors has a collection of some ansi code to better visualize strings in the terminal.
    FileService
    The class FileService has useful methods to serialize/deserialize objects adn save/load them to/from file.
    InputData
    The class InputData can read a specific data type inserted in input by the user.It also allows the possibility to make controls on the data inserted.
    KnownProblems
    The class KnownProblems has the implementation of some of the usual problem that you always forget and need to go watch the solution on StackOverflow even though you know you've already solved them.
    Menu
    The Menu class creates a menu with multiple entry supposing that zero is always the exit option.
    PrettyStrings
    The class PrettyStrings has various methods to better print strings to the terminal.
    RandomDraws
    The class RandomDraws lets you draw a specific data tipe in a pseudo-random way.
